{"lexicon" 1, "id" "com.etzhayyim.hinagata.template", "description" "A published legal-document template in the hinagata 雛形 commons (per ADR-2606111954). A fair, openly-licensed (Apache-2.0 + etzhayyim Charter Rider) reusable document anyone may copy and adapt. The canonical body text lives on IPFS (referenced by `bodyCid`, a kotoba IPFS CIDv1 raw/sha2-256 anyone can re-derive); only metadata + the clause/statute structure lives on MST. This record is NOT legal advice and NOT a substitute for counsel (G1) — it is a structural document whose clauses each cite the public law they rest on. The executable signing flow uses `com.etzhayyim.esign.envelope`.", "defs" {"main" {"type" "record", "key" "tid", "record" {"type" "object", "required" ["templateId" "title" "lang" "license" "bodyCid" "bodySha256" "stance" "createdAt"], "properties" {"lang" {"type" "string", "description" "BCP-47 language tag of this template's text, e.g. `en` / `ja`.", "maxLength" 32}, "statuteCitationUris" {"type" "array", "description" "AT URIs of the `com.etzhayyim.hinagata.statuteCitation` records binding this template's clauses to actual public law.", "maxLength" 256, "items" {"type" "string", "format" "at-uri"}}, "license" {"type" "string", "description" "SPDX id of the open license (default `Apache-2.0`) — the Charter Rider applies on top.", "maxLength" 64}, "stance" {"type" "string", "description" "DISCLOSED editorial fairness stance — a disclosed drafting choice, never a hinagata verdict (N3).", "enum" ["balanced" "neutral" "pro-consumer" "pro-weaker-party"]}, "bodyCid" {"type" "string", "format" "cid", "description" "IPFS CIDv1 (raw codec, sha2-256, base32 lower) of the canonical template body. Anyone may re-derive it with `ipfs add --cid-version=1 --raw-leaves` and verify the bytes."}, "createdAt" {"type" "string", "format" "datetime", "description" "ISO 8601 timestamp of publication."}, "clauseIds" {"type" "array", "description" "Ordered hinagata clause ids composing the template (`cl.*`).", "maxLength" 128, "items" {"type" "string", "maxLength" 128}}, "title" {"type" "string", "description" "Human title, e.g. \"Mutual Non-Disclosure Agreement\".", "maxLength" 256}, "version" {"type" "string", "description" "Semver of the template text, e.g. `1.0.0`.", "maxLength" 32}, "bodySha256" {"type" "string", "description" "0x-prefixed lowercase hex SHA-256 of the canonical body — defense-in-depth hash independent of the IPFS multihash.", "minLength" 66, "maxLength" 66}, "templateId" {"type" "string", "description" "Stable hinagata id, e.g. `tmpl.nda-mutual`.", "maxLength" 128}, "jurisdictions" {"type" "array", "description" "ISO 3166 codes / `INTL` for the jurisdictions this template is drafted for (DISCLOSED scope, never a fitness verdict for a user's situation).", "maxLength" 64, "items" {"type" "string", "maxLength" 8}}}}}}}
